 }
)
---
exit

# 配置外部访问

sudo nano /etc/mongod.conf
改变 `bindIp: 127.0.0.1` 为 `bindIp: 127.0.0.1, mongo-server-ip`
更正：修改为 `0.0.0.0`
sudo systemctl restart mongod
